Clonakilty Park Health & Leisure Club
The Ultimate Health & Fitness Club
At the Clonakilty Park Leisure Club, we are committed to providing the latest in exercise and training technology, along with the best in relaxation facilities.
The facilities listed below are exclusively for Leisure Club members and hotel residents and include:
State of the Art Gym
20m
