Download our member app to see our latest information and book classess/swim times.
Leisure Club Opening Times
Monday, Wednesday & Friday 7.00am - 9.00pm
Tuesday & Thursday 8.00am - 10.00pm
Saturday & Sunday 9.00am - 9.00pm
Children are permitted in the pool until 7.00pm
The pool is closed daily from 2.00pm - 3.00pm
During certain school holiday weeks
from 1.00 - 3.00pm weekdays.
